commit.message: Log HTTP payloads on "debug_http", not "debug".
Show upload payload on each retry attempt.
Reset both upload & download buffers before retry.
Prepare for release 2.1.1.
Fix empty payload bug when retrying an upload (issue #212).
Check for errors returned by curl_easy_setopt().
Change file tweak.
Bump wait time for nbdkit to start from 1s to 5s.
Add "--noCurlCache" flag to facilitate debugging.
Retry on 401 and 403 errors in case of rate limiting.
Try to return more meaningful error codes.
Add a few comments.
Fix bug with bulk delete HTTP requests (issue #211).
Fix bug in canonical query string when missing equals sign(s).
Also log outbound payloads when "--debug-http" flag is used.
Use CURLOPT_ACCEPT_ENCODING instead of deprecated CURLOPT_ENCODING.
Bump copyright years.
Fix incorrect error strings in several log messages.
Prepare for release 2.1.0.
Avoid unused variable warning.
Avoid sending an empty Accept-Encoding header (issue #208).
Fix broken link (#209).
Use newer HMAC API when OpenSSL >= 3.0.0 is detected.
Refactor HMAC code into util.c to facilitate upcoming changes.
Add/tweak a few assertions.
Add convenience function md5_quick().
Update obsolete config macro AM_CONFIG_HEADER() -> AC_CONFIG_HEADERS().
